              main=paste("wecare vs nfe, 3ev nfe, svt+skat, counts > ", min_counts, "\n(", sum(sel_counts), " genes x 676 cases)", sep=""))

           sel_genes.df$svt_skat_MAP[sel_counts & sel_genes.df$svt_skat_p != 0],
